summary: This mod introduces a Vampire companion into the game based on the movie character \"Selene\" from the Underworld movie series. I believe I have made a close facsimile of Kate Beckinsale given the limitations of Vanilla\'s parts. She is available in with ice blue (Vampire mode) or dark brown eyes (Human Mode) and Calculated level 45 or Auto-Level.

files.name: Selene Auto-Level Serana Eyes - Essential - Dawnguard - Clothed
files.fileName: Selene Auto-Level Serana Eyes - Essential - Dawnguard - Clothed-18378-3-0.7z
files.changelogHtml: Version 3.0 was made in the CK and NPC Editor. She is a completely new NPC so make sure you remove the old version and sorry for your loss in advance. This go around I have added two Dawnguard versions that give her the ability to use Serana's eyes. This looks great with the Underworld Vampire Eyes mod! All versions are essential and auto-level. She is still located at the Inn in Morthal and will sandbox wherever you leave her. Still marriageable and is a bit beefed up over the last version as far as spells. The best thing about this version is that it should be very clean! Easy NMM install and no BSA file.
